.TH "LIGHTNING-WALLET-SWEEP" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-wallet-sweep \- sweep all on-chain wallet funds to an address
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning wallet-sweep
.I wallet
.I destination_address
.SH DESCRIPTION
Calls
.B lightning-cli withdraw
with
.B all
to send the entire on-chain balance to
.IR destination_address .
Use with caution — this empties the on-chain wallet.
Returns an error object if the daemon is unreachable.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"ok":true,"txid":...,"tx":...}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-onchain-balance (1),
.BR lightning-wallet-backup (1)
